{
  "name": "abcd-tools-platform",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Visual action recorder for social media automation. Uses visual/coordinate-based recording instead of fragile DOM selectors.",
  "_comment_visual_recording_dependencies": "Visual recording requires these packages: html2canvas (element screenshots), pixelmatch (image comparison), tesseract.js (OCR fallback, ~2MB, optional for MVP), jimp (image processing), fuse.js (fuzzy text matching). For MVP, start with html2canvas + pixelmatch. Keep puppeteer-core (not full puppeteer) for browser automation.",
